keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy

Class FuzzyNumberTRLEFT

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.Fuzzy
      • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.FuzzyNumberTRLEFT

  • public class FuzzyNumberTRLEFT
extends Fuzzy

    Represents a right-angled triangular fuzzy number with the right-angle in left side. Each support member lower than center has the membership value of 1.0 and right represent the extreme of the triangular fuzzy number.

    Since:
    JDK1.4
